Although, you would still need to know the initial format, prior to parsing the value.

Here is a basic example of parsing the format you&#39;re using.  
You&#39;ll have to specify a _[Locale](https://docs.oracle.com/en/java/javase/20/docs/api/java.base/java/util/Locale.html)_&amp;mdash;in this example I am using _Italy_, which uses this same format.

```java
Float parseFloat(String string) {
